<p>Why is the link not working if the link is created with javascript? It only works if I make the link without the html() output</p>  <p><strong>Not working</strong></p>  <pre><code>$(".link").on('click', function(){     alert('Hello'); });  $("#link").html('&lt;a href="#" class="link"&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt;');  &lt;div id="link"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>  <p><strong>Working</strong></p>  <pre><code>$(".link").on('click', function(){     alert('Hello'); });  &lt;a href="#" class="link"&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt; </code></pre>